  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The motorcycle catches fire near the filling station",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Higurakgoda Police say that a motorcycle that got fuel from the Higurakgoda Cooperative Petrol Station and started the journey got burnt and destroyed on the road in front of the petrol station.",
        "Police say that the owner of the motorcycle that caught fire is a resident of 31 Colony, Yatialpatana, Higurakgoda area.",
        "Police say that neither the motorcyclist nor anyone staying in Polim was injured in this fire and the motorcycle was completely burnt.",
        "The employees of the petrol station tried to control the fire but could not control the fire."
      ],
